StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_DBADeleteZipcode]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@zipcode varchar(9)
as
if exists (select 1 from zip_code_assignment where zip_code = @zipcode)
begin delete from zip_code_assignment where zip_code = @zipcode
print @zipcode + ' ' + 'has been deleted'
end
else begin
print @zipcode + ' ' + 'does not exist'
end
